Fw VERIFY REGIST Original Message From SFBdirectcom To OUSTONRRCOM Sent Monday July PM Subject RE VERIFY REGIST Dear MrTycholiz Thank you for your message Fund your account today using eCheck Secure This service allows you to transfer funds from your bank account to your CSFBdirect account Go to the Customer Service section of the website click on Deposit Funds then click on the Online icon at the top of the page Follow these simple steps to transfer funds now Select an account Enter information from your checkbook and drivers license Verify the information You will receive online confirmation of your transfer request immediately The funds will be deposited in your account today and your account will reflect its receipt tomorrow This service is free to all CSFBdirect customers Cutoff time is pm ET for funds to be deposited same day After this cutoff time your funds will be deposited the following business day The bank account must be at a financial institution in the United States The check must be payable in US dollars You can deposit funds into your account with personal checks certified checks bank checks over or wired funds We do NOT ACCEPT THIRDPARTY CHECKS STARTER CHECKS MONEY ORDERS CREDIT CARD PAYMENT TEMPORARY CHECKS CREDIT CARD CHECKS BANK CHECKS UNDER or CASH Please send payment by regular mail to P O Box Newark NJ P O Box Pasadena CA Please do not send overnight checks to a P O Box IRA checks with a completed IRA Contribution form and any check sent overnight or express mail should be sent to Harborside Financial Center Plaza II Jersey City NJ South Stream Blvd Charlotte NC Please make checks payable to CSFBdirect and clearly write your account number on the face of the check Also be sure to verify that the written and numeric amounts coincide on the check prior to sending payment If you have additional questions please feel free to write back by logging into your account and sending a new message or call CSFBdirect at or TDD for the hearing impaired Sincerely Adam Lewis CSFBdirect Inc Member SIPC Member NASD If you wish to reply to this message please login to your account On our Web site go to the CUSTOMER SERVICE page and choose Email CSFBdirect If you access your account via MarketSpeed go to the HOME page and choose the Services screen on the left menu and then choose Email CSFBdirect
